quote.summary: Midea Real Estate Holding Ltd is an investment holding company principally engaged in providing property management services, asset operation business, real estate technology business and project management services business. The Company operates through four segments. The Property Management Services Business segment provides property management and value-added services for residential, commercial and other types of properties. The Asset Operation Business segment is engaged in designing, constructing, operating, or selling commercial properties and industrial parks, delivering commercial leasing and operational solutions and providing property management services. The Real Estate Technology Business segment comprises manufacturing and sales of precast concrete, modular integrated construction and other industrial components and materials as well as providing intelligent space solutions. The Project Management Services Business segment provides project management services.
